channel.description:
hey,
SRL 3.3 library is out.
comes as a .RAR file, no joke, no viruses. Enjoy!
download:
Here: http://d.turboupload.com/d/1012822/SRLv330.rar.html
Here: http://www.megaupload.com/?d=7VMLPJE3
Here: http://uploadhut.com/view.php/141801.rar
or Here: http://rapidshare.de/files/34205748/SRLv330.rar.html (Rapidshare link is dead, do not use)
ps: if you are sceptical about viruses and spyware, it comes as a .RAR file, so you can scan it and everything, I promise this is a legit release of the SRL library 3.3.
[u]SETUP INSTRUCTIONS:[/u] Just unzip the [u]whole thing[/u] to your root scar folder and then run the [u]readme.scar[/u], thats all for setup!
